setCaptureWebworkData

public void setCaptureWebworkData(boolean captureWebworkData)
Method used to capture information like assignment points, due date(end date), open date(start date) from the webwork and present it to the instructor / TA when assigning the content in assignmet.jsp page. Thus this method pulls information from webwork,(if not available, instructor has to set dates which will be written back to webwork) and thus synchronizes information between webwork & blackboard.

Parameters:
captureWebworkData - Flag to capture information from webwork.
